# Business Viewpoint – SoilSense

## 1. Overview

The Business Viewpoint describes the SoilSense system from a business perspective, focusing on how the capabilities of the IoT architecture generate value for stakeholders, support operational objectives, and enable future service evolution.

This viewpoint follows the principles defined in ISO/IEC 30141:2024 and addresses the concerns of business managers, system owners, architects, and end users.

---

