## 9. Business Implications

### Operational Efficiency

Automation reduces repetitive manual monitoring activities and allows personnel to focus on higher-value tasks.

### Improved Visibility

Continuous access to environmental information improves situational awareness.

### Better Decision Making

Historical and real-time data support informed operational decisions.

### Scalability

The architecture can accommodate additional devices and services as requirements evolve.

### Interoperability

Open standards facilitate integration with future systems and platforms.

### Availability

OpenThread provides self-healing capabilities that improve service continuity.

### Sustainability

The use of open technologies reduces dependency on proprietary ecosystems and supports long-term maintainability.

